 New Functionality of 0.12.12 Terraform:
  - No more string interpolation for attributes
  - 'For' loop expressions and splat operators.
  - Dynamic blocks (Example usage: Ingress rules and engress rule)
  
Splat Expressions:
 - > If var.list is list of objects and all have id attribute.
 - > [for o in var.list : o.id] equivalent splat expression var.list[*].id
 
 
 
You can use "tfswitch" command to use latest version for Linux.
- terraform state list : list of resources
- terraform state show :                                             
- terraform init : command used to initiliaze a working directory containg Terraform  config file.
- terraform get  : command used to download or update modulues.
